{"title":"山村医生","authors":["吴家祥"],"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":10,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"山村医生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吴家祥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安家在一寨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寨寨都有家；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一路清脆的歌声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一口新学的彝话。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"药箱儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长年累月肩上挎；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茅草路上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走尽了秋冬春夏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"累了——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拧几帕山泉把汗擦；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饿了——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃几口炒面荞粑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走东村治疟疾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到西寨接娃娃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深夜出诊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"擎一支熊熊的火把。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为大娘熬汤煎药，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给产妇煮饭烧茶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命热情涌心怀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"常把彝族人民牵挂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灯下常读毛主席著作，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地里勤学种庄稼；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗红心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两手茧巴；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要学伟大的白求恩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红在山岈，专在山岈！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}